<p>I am using Apache POI 3.12:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;dependency&gt;     &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.poi&lt;/groupId&gt;     &lt;artifactId&gt;poi&lt;/artifactId&gt;     &lt;version&gt;3.12&lt;/version&gt; &lt;/dependency&gt;  &lt;dependency&gt;     &lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.poi&lt;/groupId&gt;     &lt;artifactId&gt;poi-ooxml&lt;/artifactId&gt;     &lt;version&gt;3.12&lt;/version&gt; &lt;/dependency&gt; </code></pre>  <p>How do I change the font within a pivot table? Examining the generated .xlsx after changing the font for one cell (I7) to size 8pt shows the following changes:</p>  <p>styles.xml, within the  tag as the 2nd entry:</p>  <pre><code>&lt;font&gt;     &lt;sz val="8"/&gt;     &lt;color indexed="8"/&gt;     &lt;name val="Calibri"/&gt;     &lt;family val="2"/&gt;     &lt;scheme val="minor"/&gt; &lt;/font&gt;  within the &lt;cellXfs&gt; tag as the 5th entry: &lt;xf numFmtId="0" fontId="1" fillId="0" borderId="0" xfId="0" applyNumberFormat="1" applyFont="1"/&gt;  New tag: dxfs: &lt;dxfs count="1"&gt;     &lt;dxf&gt;         &lt;font&gt;             &lt;sz val="8"/&gt;         &lt;/font&gt;     &lt;/dxf&gt; &lt;/dxfs&gt; </code></pre>  <p>pivottable.xml</p>  <pre><code>&lt;formats count="1"&gt;     &lt;format dxfId="0"&gt;         &lt;pivotArea collapsedLevelsAreSubtotals="1" fieldPosition="0"&gt;         &lt;references count="2"&gt;         &lt;reference field="4294967294" count="1" selected="0"&gt;         &lt;x v="0"/&gt;         &lt;/reference&gt;         &lt;reference field="0" count="1"&gt;         &lt;x v="0"/&gt;         &lt;/reference&gt;         &lt;/references&gt;         &lt;/pivotArea&gt;     &lt;/format&gt; &lt;/formats&gt; </code></pre>  <p>sheet1.xml</p>  <pre><code>&lt;c r="I7" s="4"&gt; </code></pre>  <p>Note: I may close this as a self-answer as I am still trying to solve it myself.  However, I've been at this for almost a week. <a href="https://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/poi/trunk/src/examples/src/org/apache/poi/xssf/usermodel/examples/CreatePivot